USER AUTHENTICATION OVERHAUL                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                                
## Overview                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                
Replace legacy session-based auth with OAuth 2.0 + PKCE.                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                
## Goals                                                                                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                
• Eliminate session token storage issues                                                                                                                        
• Support SSO via SAML/OIDC                                                                                                                                     
• Reduce login friction by 40%                                                                                                                                  
                                                                                                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                                
